{"route":"/docs/reference/layout/relative/","title":"Relative Length","description":"Documentation for the Relative Length type.","part":null,"outline":[{"id":"summary","name":"概要","children":[]},{"id":"例","name":"例","children":[]}],"body":{"kind":"type","content":{"name":"relative","title":"Relative Length","keywords":[],"oneliner":"既知の長さに対する相対的な長さ。","details":"<p>既知の長さに対する相対的な長さ。</p>\n<p>この型は<a href=\"/docs/reference/layout/length/\" title=\"length\">length</a>と<a href=\"/docs/reference/layout/ratio/\" title=\"ratio\">ratio</a>の組み合わせです。\nこれは長さと百分率の加減算の結果になります。\n相対長さが想定されているあらゆる箇所で長さまたは百分率を単体でも指定可能です。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例\">例</h2>\n<div class=\"previewed-code\"><pre><code><span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">rect</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>width<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">100%</span> <span class=\"typ-op\">-</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">50pt</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"typ-punct\">#</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-num\">100%</span> <span class=\"typ-op\">-</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">50pt</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">.</span><span class=\"typ-pol\">length</span> <span class=\"typ-escape\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"typ-punct\">#</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-num\">100%</span> <span class=\"typ-op\">-</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">50pt</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">.</span><span class=\"typ-pol\">ratio</span>\n</code></pre><div class=\"preview\"><img src=\"/docs/assets/78c4d2ff0209fbcacbccfe80f80eb03c.png\" alt=\"Preview\"></div></div>\n<p>相対長さは以下のフィールドを持ちます。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>length</code>: 長さ成分。</li>\n<li><code>ratio</code>: 百分率成分。</li>\n</ul>","constructor":null,"scope":[]}}}